title: Welcome to Club Dub
itunes:title: Welcome to Club Dub
description:
The Good Morning Football Crew share their biggest takeaways from week 4 of the NFL season and looks ahead to week 5 by answering who's the most surprising 3-1 team? The gang also discusses what we learned from week 4. Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Peter Schrager, and Kyle Brandt give you their underappreciated storylines. Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
